  <span id="freeText13773453234202753368" style="display:none">WHAT...<br /><br />JUST... what!?<br /><br />I can't even...<br /><br />My summary of this book is: WTF, Cathy?!<br /><br />I mean, I liked it and I'll definitely finish this saga, for I am too invested, but I don't know, this book is just TOO MUCH.</span>
