<div id="review_2822426127" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2822426127" />
    <a title="Chantal" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/31954777-chantal"><img alt="Chantal" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1586070858p2/31954777.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2822426127?book_show_action=true">May 20, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chantal" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chantal" href="/user/show/31954777-chantal">Chantal</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31954777-chantal?shelf=book-cabinet-read">book-cabinet-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2822426127" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10192756626330196165">After Flowers in the attic, I couldn&apos;t stop myself from reading this book. I had to read it, never knew there was a part 2 and more. I liked it, but sometimes I was disappointed. I didn&apos;t like the endless sex scenes and sex hunkering. Not everything in life revolves around sex lol! The rest of the book was great and it had a good story. I am glad I could read after so many years. So it will get 4 points. I can&apos;t wait to start part 3.<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1558367045i/27545601.jpg' width='300' height='300' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
  <span id="freeText10192756626330196165" style="display:none">After Flowers in the attic, I couldn't stop myself from reading this book. I had to read it, never knew there was a part 2 and more. I liked it, but sometimes I was disappointed. I didn't like the endless sex scenes and sex hunkering. Not everything in life revolves around sex lol! The rest of the book was great and it had a good story. I am glad I could read after so many years. So it will get 4 points. I can't wait to start part 3.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1558367045i/27545601.jpg" width="300" height="300" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
  <a data-text-id="10192756626330196165" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

